Esther Dale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esther_Dale 0 Esther Dale (November 10, 1885 – July 23, 1961) was an American actress, best known perhaps for her role as Aunt Genevieve in the 1935 Shirley Temple vehicle, Curly Top.
